{"tid":168470,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"和記寬頻用戶請進","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T02:09:31.000Z","uid":39085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1ced7dbe22400bc862bf6434e5b53428d77b75","tid":168470,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"用緊和記100M寬頻, 發覺上網愈黎愈慢<br />\n然後上 <a href=\"http://beta.speedtest.net/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeta.speedtest.net%2F%20&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=67f71ad5\" target=\"_blank\">http://beta.speedtest.net/ </a><br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://speedtest.ofca.gov.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspeedtest.ofca.gov.hk%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2e50c402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://speedtest.ofca.gov.hk/</a><br />\n[/url]呢兩個網測速啦, 仆你個街, 下載速度一半都冇, 有時得幾mb, 上載就正常(有80-90M)...wifi 仲慘, 爆格連線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1Q78n0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1Q78n0.jpg&h=9aa0ae7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打去客服問啦, 叫我上佢和記個網測先最準 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.speedmeter.com.hk/html/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.speedmeter.com.hk%2Fhtml%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6761a6ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.speedmeter.com.hk/html/</a> 大家可以試下...<br />\n最神奇既事出現鳥, 每一次都會90M以上...同時間地另外兩個測速網都少一半以上。跟住就左賴右賴：<br />\n1. OFCA個官網只係參考, 唔撚準, 可能而家多人用緊 <br />\n2. 叫你熄左ROUTER先, 會影響 <br />\n3. 可能你上既網/GAME 問題 <br />\n4. 可能你屋企電腦硬件問題<br />\n.......................<br />\n<br />\n我屋企3部電腦, PS4, IPAD 電話全部都有問題? 試過熄哂router, 只插一條lan 入電腦/ps4, 咪一鳩樣。我ps4 參與分享遊玩每次都話我太慢連唔到...我細佬LOL每次都lag 到仆街...<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求指教<br />\n我係咪應該直頭搵消委會算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><del>我知錯唔應該揀和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del></span>"},{"pid":"812e3cd34dd6a133b1ff9924d8f8980099a12a91","tid":168470,"uid":41446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:57:02.000Z","msg":"屌我都覺慢咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f849f04267a3f44b94834ba1664f4d781a8378","tid":168470,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T06:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我都覺慢咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇測下個速度<br />\n佢官方提供每次測都話90幾M, 但明顯地用落冇<br />\n尋晚打fifa online 斷左三場線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪屌完佢會仲差左"},{"pid":"c46aa9a905282a8769e322f163a50e81b6ab5bf8","tid":168470,"uid":93570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72b9b45217f7c90e1b322437a3a9f65fb748dd78","tid":168470,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"和記不嬲狗也不屌"},{"pid":"b46c8694625df43912cea66494728b995ad328cd","tid":168470,"uid":52833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"100M個PLAN份約有速度保證<br />\n可以打上去嘈尻佢地"},{"pid":"d6fc04ef3294cbd5682e0ff417bf95d9acd5785c","tid":168470,"uid":92001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d656aaf26992aa4d075ef82993cfe1842ee84bc","tid":168470,"uid":44783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"和記都用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\